<lb n="0918b11" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1402</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0918b12" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0918007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>消除一切閃電障難隨求如意陀
<lb n="0918b13" ed="T"/>羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0918b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0918b15" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0918008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0918008"><lem wit="【大】">西</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西</rdg></app>天北印度烏填曩國帝釋宮寺
<lb n="0918b16" ed="T"/>三藏傳法大師賜紫沙門<note n="0918009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0918009"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0918b17" ed="T"/>施護奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0918b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918b1801">如是我聞。一時佛在舍衛國精舍之中。爾時
<lb n="0918b19" ed="T"/>世尊告尊者阿難陀言。汝今諦聽有消除一
<lb n="0918b20" ed="T"/>切閃電障難隨求如意陀羅尼經。過去如來
<lb n="0918b21" ed="T"/>無上正等正覺之所宣說。如我今者痡`悲
<lb n="0918b22" ed="T"/><note n="0918010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00517;＝愍【三】</note><note n="0918010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00517;＝愍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0918010"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00517;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">愍</rdg></app>。為欲利益<note n="0918011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宋本天上人間四字闕</note><note n="0918011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天上人間〕四字－【宋】</note><app n="0918011"><lem wit="【大】">天上人間</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>一切群生得安樂
<lb n="0918b23" ed="T"/>故。亦復宣說。</p>
<lb n="0918b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918b2401">阿難陀言如是世尊願樂欲聞。</p>
<lb n="0918b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918b2501">世尊告言。阿難陀東方有電名阿伽曩<note place="inline"><note n="0918012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宋言＝此言【明】下同</note><app n="0918012"><lem wit="【大】">宋言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">此言</rdg></app>無厚</note>
<lb n="0918b26" ed="T"/>南方有電名舍多嚕<note place="inline">宋言順流</note>西方有電名放光明。
<lb n="0918b27" ed="T"/>北方有電名燥那麼尼<note place="inline">宋言百生樹</note>。阿難陀若有族
<lb n="0918b28" ed="T"/>姓男族姓女。知此明名號之者。彼所住方無
<lb n="0918b29" ed="T"/>此一切雷電驚怖。若所住處有如是閃電。但
<pb n="0918c" id="T21.1402.0918c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0918c01" ed="T"/>書此真言安置彼處一切閃電而不能發。</p>
<lb n="0918c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c0201">爾時世尊即說此<note n="0918013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捺＝&CB00706;【三】＊</note><note n="0918013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捺＝&CB00706;【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0918013"><lem wit="【大】">捺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00706;</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>弭拏真言章句曰。</p>
<lb n="0918c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c0301" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引一</note>&CB00135;彌&CB00135;泯達&CB00942;<note place="inline">二</note>怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0918c04" ed="T"/>路<note place="inline">去引</note>迦<note place="inline">去引</note>路<note place="inline">去引</note>枳&CB00135;<note place="inline">三</note>戌<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00256;播<note place="inline">上引</note>抳<note place="inline">上</note>
<lb n="0918c05" ed="T"/>&CB00135;<note place="inline">四</note>囉乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">牟含<note n="0918014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝切【明】＊</note><app n="0918014"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>稱名五</note>薩&CB00085;尾
<lb n="0918c06" ed="T"/>&CB00135;庾<note place="inline">二合</note>那婆<note place="inline">二合</note>曳毘藥<note place="inline">二合六</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引七</note></p>
<lb n="0918c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c0701">爾時聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。與自眾等皆來
<lb n="0918c08" ed="T"/>集會一面而坐。時觀自在菩薩即從坐起。白
<lb n="0918c09" ed="T"/>言世尊我亦說此正法。</p>
<lb n="0918c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c1001"><app source="0918013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">捺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00706;</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>弭拏真言章句曰。</p>
<lb n="0918c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c1101" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引一</note>尾曩<note place="inline">引</note>舍&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底也<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0918c12" ed="T"/>哩替<note place="inline">二合</note>計<note place="inline">二</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底也<note place="inline">二合</note>彌怛&CB00942;<note place="inline">二合三</note>秣
<lb n="0918c13" ed="T"/>第穆訖諦<note place="inline">四</note>尾麼禮<note place="inline">五</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去引</note>娑迦<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0918c14" ed="T"/>&CB00942;<note place="inline">六</note>頞拏&CB00942;<note place="inline">七</note>半拏&CB00942;<note place="inline">八</note>悉吠<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">九</note>半拏囉
<lb n="0918c15" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">去</note>枲&CB00135;<note place="inline">十</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note>帝迦囉<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00256;<note place="inline">十一</note>劫畢羅&CB00457;<note place="inline">上</note>
<lb n="0918c16" ed="T"/>&CB00344;&CB00256;<note place="inline">十二</note>乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>那地穆乞史<note place="inline">二合十三</note>囉乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0918c17" ed="T"/>囉乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">十四</note>薩<note place="inline">轉舌</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>迦<note place="inline">上引</note>&CB00256;蜜&CB00069;
<lb n="0918c18" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>底庾<note place="inline">二合</note>佩<note place="inline">上</note>曳毘藥<note place="inline">二合十五</note>麼<note place="inline">引上</note>銘<note place="inline"><note n="0918015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十六＝上【宋】【元】，（上）＋十【明】</note><app n="0918015"><lem wit="【大】">十六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">上</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上十六</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0918c19" ed="T"/>跛舍演<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;<note place="inline">十七</note>薩<note place="inline">轉舌</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>迦&CB00256;蜜&CB00069;<note place="inline">二合</note>底
<lb n="0918c20" ed="T"/>也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">入十八</note>阿<note place="inline">上</note>哩野<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00085;路<note place="inline">上引</note>枳諦濕
<lb n="0918c21" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉帝惹<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十九</note></p>
<lb n="0918c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c2201">爾時金剛手祕密主。向佛合掌恭敬白世尊
<lb n="0918c23" ed="T"/>言。我亦說此正法陀羅尼真言章句曰。</p>
<lb n="0918c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c2401" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引一</note>母&CB00135;母&CB00135;<note place="inline">二</note>母&CB00135;麼底<note place="inline">三</note>麼
<lb n="0918c25" ed="T"/>底素麼底<note place="inline">四</note>麼賀<note place="inline">引</note>麼底<note place="inline">五</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引六</note>
<lb n="0918c26" ed="T"/>麼<note place="inline">引</note>帶囉曩<note place="inline">二合引</note>悉底<note place="inline">二合</note>播崩<note place="inline">去聲七</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0918c27" ed="T"/>合</note>播抳囉舍<note place="inline">上八</note>&CB00135;哩<note place="inline">二合</note>茶<note place="inline">上</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引九</note></p>
<lb n="0918c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0918c2801">世尊我此章句名無能勝。若有憶念受持書
<lb n="0918c29" ed="T"/>寫供養者。我常擁護一切怖畏。一切中<note n="0918016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夭＝天【宋】</note><app n="0918016"><lem wit="【大】">夭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">天</rdg></app>
<pb n="0919a" id="T21.1402.0919a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0919a01" ed="T"/>即得解脫。</p>
<lb n="0919a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a0201">爾時娑訶世界主大梵天王。白言世尊我亦
<lb n="0919a03" ed="T"/>說此正法陀羅尼真言章句。為欲利益安樂
<lb n="0919a04" ed="T"/>諸有情故。即說陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0919a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a0501" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引一</note>醯里蜜里<note place="inline">二</note>只里娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0919a06" ed="T"/>賀<note n="0919001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三〕－【三】</note><note n="0919001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔三〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0919001"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾麼<note place="inline">二合</note>布&CB00942;<note place="inline">四</note>麼賀<note place="inline">引</note>沒囉
<lb n="0919a07" ed="T"/><note place="inline"><note n="0919002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝三【明】</note><app n="0919002"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">三</rdg></app>合</note>憾麼<note place="inline">二合引</note>抳<note place="inline">五</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾麼<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00859;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>陛
<lb n="0919a08" ed="T"/><note place="inline">六</note>布瑟崩<note place="inline">去二合</note>僧<note place="inline">去</note>娑哆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00942;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引七</note></p>
<lb n="0919a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a0901">世尊此名梵天難拏陀羅尼。能救護於一切
<lb n="0919a10" ed="T"/>中夭。獲得長壽。一切罪業皆悉消滅。</p>
<lb n="0919a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a1101">爾時帝釋天主向世尊所。合掌恭敬白世尊
<lb n="0919a12" ed="T"/>言。我亦說此正法陀羅尼真言章句曰。</p>
<lb n="0919a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a1301" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引一</note>沒馱麼蹬<note place="inline">上</note>膩<note place="inline">二</note>麼&CB00135;&CB00135;<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0919a14" ed="T"/>矯<note place="inline">魚夭<app source="0918014" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>哩巘<note place="inline">引</note>馱哩<note place="inline">四</note>贊拏<note place="inline">上引</note>里麼<note place="inline">引</note>蹬<note place="inline">去</note>儗<note place="inline">五</note>
<lb n="0919a15" ed="T"/>卜迦枲<note place="inline">六</note>娑<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00256;沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">七</note>呬<note place="inline">上</note>曩麼第<note place="inline">引八</note>
<lb n="0919a16" ed="T"/>跢<note place="inline">引</note>囉抳<note place="inline">九</note>麼姤<note place="inline">引</note>里&CB00135;計<note place="inline">十</note>作訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0919a17" ed="T"/>枳<note place="inline">十一</note>舍&CB00085;哩捨<note place="inline">引上</note>&CB00085;哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十二</note></p>
<lb n="0919a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a1801">世尊我此明句名金剛坐。所有一切驚怖及
<lb n="0919a19" ed="T"/>諸中夭。而無障礙悉得解脫。</p>
<lb n="0919a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a2001">爾時持國天王增長天王廣目天王多聞天
<lb n="0919a21" ed="T"/>王。合掌向佛白言世尊。我等亦說此正法陀
<lb n="0919a22" ed="T"/>羅尼章句曰。</p>
<lb n="0919a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a2301" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引去一</note>補瑟閉<note place="inline">二合</note>蘇補瑟閉<note place="inline">二合二</note>
<lb n="0919a24" ed="T"/>度跛波哩賀<note place="inline"><note n="0919003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＝上【三】</note><note n="0919003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引＝上【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0919003"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">上</rdg></app></note>&CB00942;<note place="inline">三</note>阿<note place="inline">上</note>哩野<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>舍
<lb n="0919a25" ed="T"/>悉諦<note place="inline">四</note>扇<note place="inline">引</note>帝&CB00135;<note place="inline">泥逸<app source="0918014" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>穆訖帝<note place="inline">二合五</note>蟒<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00859;禮曳
<lb n="0919a26" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合六</note>&CB01433;<note n="0919004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01836;＝瀾【三】</note><note n="0919004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01836;＝瀾【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0919004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB01836;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">瀾</rdg></app>抳也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00859;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>陛<note place="inline">七</note>窣&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>膩<note place="inline">上</note>娑
<lb n="0919a27" ed="T"/>多<note place="inline">二合</note>尾膩<note place="inline">上</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引八</note></p>
<lb n="0919a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919a2801">世尊我等四王如上所說真言章句名無怖
<lb n="0919a29" ed="T"/>畏。於諸怖<app><lem wit="【CBETA】">畏</lem><rdg wit="【大】">異</rdg></app>而作擁護。一切壽命令無中夭。</p>
<pb n="0919b" id="T21.1402.0919b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0919b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919b0101">爾時娑&CB00344;嚕龍王麼曩悉吠<note place="inline">二合</note>龍王電光龍
<lb n="0919b02" ed="T"/>王無熱惱池龍王。電舌龍王百光龍王等。亦
<lb n="0919b03" ed="T"/>向世尊前合掌恭敬住立一面。</p>
<lb n="0919b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919b0401">世尊告言有此如意章句之處。擁護一切閃
<lb n="0919b05" ed="T"/>電障難。亦能救護一切中夭攝除諸毒。一切
<lb n="0919b06" ed="T"/>羯祛那吠哆拏。作不吉祥事者亦悉破壞。汝
<lb n="0919b07" ed="T"/>等諦聽當發慈心。汝等龍趣之中。各生嗔恚
<lb n="0919b08" ed="T"/>我慢貢高當應降伏。諸龍白言云何降伏。世
<lb n="0919b09" ed="T"/>尊答言我有陀羅尼。令汝等龍我慢貢高心
<lb n="0919b10" ed="T"/>便止息。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0919b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919b1101" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引去一</note>阿<note place="inline">上</note>惹&CB00942;<note place="inline">二</note>麼麼&CB00942;<note place="inline">三</note>阿蜜
<lb n="0919b12" ed="T"/>&CB00069;<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">四</note>阿乞叉<note place="inline">二合引</note>曳<note place="inline">五</note>阿尾也<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">六</note>奔
<lb n="0919b13" ed="T"/>抳也<note place="inline">二合</note>跛哩也<note place="inline">二合引</note>曳<note place="inline">七</note>薩&CB00085;播跛<note place="inline">八</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0919b14" ed="T"/>舍麼&CB00135;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引九</note>阿<note place="inline">引上</note>哩野半<note place="inline">引</note>拏<note place="inline">十</note>
<lb n="0919b15" ed="T"/>燥播<note place="inline">引</note>枳<note place="inline">上</note>曳娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十一</note>印<app source="0918013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">捺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00706;</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>設
<lb n="0919b16" ed="T"/>寧<note place="inline">上</note>曳娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十二</note>銘<note place="inline">上</note>伽<note place="inline">上</note>設寧<note place="inline">上</note>娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0919b17" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十三</note></p>
<lb n="0919b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919b1801">世尊告言。若有男子女人。於此真言章句。受
<lb n="0919b19" ed="T"/>持讀誦書寫供養者。彼諸龍神閃電等怖不
<lb n="0919b20" ed="T"/>能為害。亦無根毒及和合毒。諸所作毒悉不
<lb n="0919b21" ed="T"/>能害我等及一切眾生故。</p>
<lb n="0919b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919b2201">爾時大梵天王及天帝釋。護世四王諸龍王
<lb n="0919b23" ed="T"/>等。讚言善哉善哉賢者。為欲利益安樂多數
<lb n="0919b24" ed="T"/>諸群生故。善說此正法<app source="0918013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">捺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00706;</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>彌拏真言
<lb n="0919b25" ed="T"/>章句。我等一心受持。佛說此經時。一切世間
<lb n="0919b26" ed="T"/>天人阿蘇&CB02255;犍闥婆等及諸大眾。聞佛所說
<lb n="0919b27" ed="T"/>歡喜奉行。</p>
<lb n="0919b28" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>消除一切閃<note n="0919005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">電＋（障難）【明】</note><app n="0919005"><lem wit="【大】">電</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">電障難</rdg></app>隨求如意陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
